#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.36"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.36:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.36:0.2"
msgid "4. Upālivagga"
msgstr "4. With Upāli"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.36:0.3"
msgid "36. Sāmaṇerasutta"
msgstr "36. A Novice"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.36:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Katihi nu kho, bhante, dhammehi samannāgatena bhikkhunā sāmaṇero "
"upaṭṭhāpetabbo”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, how many qualities should a mendicant have to be attended on by a "
"novice?”"

msgctxt "an10.36:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Dasahi kho, upāli, dhammehi samannāgatena bhikkhunā sāmaṇero upaṭṭhāpetabbo."
msgstr ""
"“Upāli, a mendicant should have ten qualities to be attended on by a novice."

msgctxt "an10.36:1.3"
msgid "Katamehi dasahi?"
msgstr "What ten?"

msgctxt "an10.36:1.4"
msgid "Idhupāli, bhikkhu sīlavā hoti … pe … samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu;"
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant is ethical …"

msgctxt "an10.36:1.5"
msgid "bahussuto hoti … pe … diṭṭhiyā suppaṭividdhā;"
msgstr "They’re learned …"

msgctxt "an10.36:1.6"
msgid ""
"pātimokkhaṃ kho panassa vitthārena svāgataṃ hoti suvibhattaṃ suppavattaṃ "
"suvinicchitaṃ suttaso anubyañjanaso;"
msgstr ""
"Both monastic codes have been passed down to them in detail, well analyzed, "
"well mastered, well judged in both the rules and accompanying material."

msgctxt "an10.36:1.7"
msgid "paṭibalo hoti gilānaṃ upaṭṭhātuṃ vā upaṭṭhāpetuṃ vā;"
msgstr "They’re able to care for the sick or get someone else to do so."

msgctxt "an10.36:1.8"
msgid "paṭibalo hoti anabhiratiṃ vūpakāsetuṃ vā vūpakāsāpetuṃ vā;"
msgstr "They’re able to settle dissatisfaction or get someone else to do so."

msgctxt "an10.36:1.9"
msgid "paṭibalo hoti uppannaṃ kukkuccaṃ dhammato vinodetuṃ;"
msgstr "They’re able to dispel remorse when it has come up."

msgctxt "an10.36:1.10"
msgid "paṭibalo hoti uppannaṃ diṭṭhigataṃ dhammato vivecetuṃ;"
msgstr ""
"They’re able to rationally dissuade someone from misconceptions that come up."

msgctxt "an10.36:1.11"
msgid "paṭibalo hoti adhisīle samādapetuṃ;"
msgstr "They’re able to encourage someone in the higher ethics,"

msgctxt "an10.36:1.12"
msgid "paṭibalo hoti adhicitte samādapetuṃ;"
msgstr "the higher mind,"

msgctxt "an10.36:1.13"
msgid "paṭibalo hoti adhipaññāya samādapetuṃ."
msgstr "and the higher wisdom."

msgctxt "an10.36:1.14"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, upāli, dasahi dhammehi samannāgatena bhikkhunā sāmaṇero "
"upaṭṭhāpetabbo”ti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant should have these ten qualities to be attended on by a novice.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.36:1.15"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
